title: Weirdstone of Brisingamen (Pinnacle Storyteller)
description:
The Weirdstone of Brisingamen by Alan Garner (abridged)
Read by George Layton

Series: Pinnacle Storyteller
Published 1980

Format: Abridged for a single audio cassette
Running time: Approx 90 mins

Mp3 Recorded in Audacity
Bitrate: 192 kbps
Front cover included


From Wikipedia:

The Weirdstone of Brisingamen is a children's fantasy novel written by the English author Alan Garner.

George Layton was born in Bradford, West Riding of Yorkshire and is an English actor, director and author.

(First audibook I owned :) it's abridged excerpts for a single audio tape but a great reading)
